The following day, in order to meet the client,

48
00:05:02,165 --> 00:05:05,565
we went to the Beika Department Store.

49
00:05:05,565 --> 00:05:10,065
FBI agent, Jodie was also there.

50
00:05:10,065 --> 00:05:12,665
The person she is searching for is most probably,

51
00:05:12,665 --> 00:05:13,865
that man.

52
00:05:18,065 --> 00:05:23,465
"The 13 Black Suggestions"

53
00:05:23,465 --> 00:05:25,665
"Beika Department Store"

54
